# Library Management System🤞

_🙌This project is a_ **Library Management System** _featuring an admin login page and backend API for authentication. It allows admins to log in, manage books, and track user activities🥳._ ~ {_**Credit- Vanshika Sinha**_}

## Features
- **Admin Login**: _Secure login for administrators to access the backend and manage the library system._ 🔐
- **User Authentication**: _Allows users to log in with their credentials to interact with the system._ 🧑‍💻
- **Admin Dashboard**: _View and manage library books, users, and issued books through the admin dashboard._ 📊
- **Book Issuing System**: _Admin can issue books to users and track issued books._ 📚
- **User Homepage**: _Users can see the list of available books and check their issued book status._ 🏠
- **Customizable UI**: _Vibrant, modern design with background images and responsive layout._ 🎨
- **Error Handling**: _Displays error messages for invalid login attempts or server issues._ ⚠️
- **Backend Authentication**: _Node.js-based API with JSON response for authentication requests._ 🔌
- **Dynamic Input Fields**: _Interactive forms for admin login and user management._ 📝
- **Frontend-Backend Integration**: _Seamless communication between the frontend (HTML/CSS) and backend (Node.js)._ 🔗
- **Security Features**: _Basic authentication mechanism to prevent unauthorized access to the admin panel._ 🛡️
- **Extensible Architecture**: _The system is easily extendable to include more features like notifications, advanced search, etc._ 🔧

